  </div>

  <p>Dear <strong>User</strong>,</p>

  <p>Welcome to Sapphire! Your OTP for signup is provided below. Do not share this OTP with anyone. It is valid for 10 minutes.</p>

  <div class="otp-container">
    <p>Your verification code:</p>
    <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
    <div class="timer-box">
      <span style="margin-right: 8px;">‚è±Ô∏è</span>
