        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div style="display: flex;">
      <div style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 28px; height: 28px; border-radius: 50%; background-color: var(--success); color: var(--white); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 600; margin-right: 16px; margin-top: 4px; font-size: 14px;">4</div>
      <div style="flex-grow: 1;">
        <h4 style="font-weight: 600; color: var(--success); margin-bottom: 4px;">Account Activation</h4>
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-medium); margin: 0;">
